## 7. Project Structure

```
src/
├── components/          # Reusable UI (Button, Card, Header, Navbar, Footer, Accordion)
├── Views/               # Page-level components
│   ├── Home.tsx
│   ├── About.tsx
│   └── Projects/        # Project case studies (DesignSystems, Arine, Precisely, etc.)
├── styles/              # Global animations, logo styles
├── App.tsx
├── main.tsx
└── index.css            # Root tokens, base styles

public/
├── assets/              # Images, logos, project assets
├── Fonts/               # Custom fonts (Wosker)
└── *.png, *.svg         # Root-level images
```

